{"tid":1876330,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"廿九歲人仲玩職業性失蹤。。。。。。","createTime":"2020-02-12T10:30:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-18T17:34:47.000Z","uid":7439,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"06d4f2e4e50058b4bf42b7c704ebdae882ea59cc","tid":1876330,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T10:30:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202002/12/P2020021200444.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F202002%2F12%2FP2020021200444.htm&d=DYxn%2BwEapY32uLV96Ej4GMkuRvkIHaPazTq7BlmTy1I%3D&h=b3cdedac\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202002/12/P2020021200444.htm</a><br />\n警方呼籲市民提供田心失蹤男子消息（附圖）<br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n<img src=\"https://gia.info.gov.hk/general/202002/12/P2020021200444_photo_1171370.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgia.info.gov.hk%2Fgeneral%2F202002%2F12%2FP2020021200444_photo_1171370.jpg&h=49b6ec2c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2417078/org/fb899704e7f82cc0caa1a8f7ed8e274d.jpg/5c61GLhOKxme3TDMTqHf1wceh4NK9OE4cGc6JXBnOiU\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2417078%2Forg%2Ffb899704e7f82cc0caa1a8f7ed8e274d.jpg%2F5c61GLhOKxme3TDMTqHf1wceh4NK9OE4cGc6JXBnOiU&h=a8d07f64&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n  警方今日（二月十二日）呼籲市民提供一名在田心失蹤男子的消息。<br />\n<br />\n  二十九歲男子林治宏於二月六日下午離開其位於沙角邨的住所後便告失蹤，其監護人昨日（二月十一日）向警方報案。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">  他身高約一點七米，體重約五十六公斤，瘦身材，長面型，黃皮膚及蓄短直黑髮。他最後露面時身穿迷彩外套、米色長褲及藍色拖鞋。</span><br />\n<br />\n  任何人如有該失蹤男子的消息或曾見過他，請致電三六六一 一一七三或六○九九 三八三○或電郵至rmpu-nts-2@police.gov.hk與新界南總區失蹤人口調查組，或與任何一間警署聯絡。<br />\n <br />\n完<br />\n2020年2月12日（星期三）<br />\n香港時間15時17分"},{"pid":"fece5d33bdba489b80650d4237fbb56519067beb","tid":1876330,"uid":7439,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T10:30:46.000Z","msg":"2019年12月15日凌晨 離開沙角邨住所後失蹤<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">2020年1月14日下午</span> 自行返回其住所<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202001/15/P2020011500406.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F202001%2F15%2FP2020011500406.htm&d=DYxn%2BwEapY32uLV96Ej4GMkuRvkIHaPazTq7BlmTy1I%3D&h=b6313d48\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202001/15/P2020011500406.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n2019年2月6日晚上  離開沙角邨住所後失蹤<br />\n2019年2月14日下午 打鼓嶺文錦渡路被尋回<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201902/18/P2019021800651.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F201902%2F18%2FP2019021800651.htm&d=DYxn%2BwEapY32uLV96Ej4GMkuRvkIHaPazTq7BlmTy1I%3D&h=72790e10\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201902/18/P2019021800651.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年4月30日凌晨 沙角邨最後露面後失蹤<br />\n2018年10月16日下午 自行向警方銷案<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201810/18/P2018101800404.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F201810%2F18%2FP2018101800404.htm&d=DYxn%2BwEapY32uLV96Ej4GMkuRvkIHaPazTq7BlmTy1I%3D&h=dc431241\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201810/18/P2018101800404.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n2017年10月13日下午 沙角邨最後露面後失蹤<br />\n2017年11月4日下午 朋友陪同下到沙田警署銷案<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201711/04/P2017110400827.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F201711%2F04%2FP2017110400827.htm&d=DYxn%2BwEapY32uLV96Ej4GMkuRvkIHaPazTq7BlmTy1I%3D&h=d596d580\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201711/04/P2017110400827.htm</a>"},{"pid":"8229e58ac439b22d2d547a2deeabf445594e6254","tid":1876330,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T10:32:22.000Z","msg":"核彈<br />\n<br />\n警方呼籲市民提供荃灣失